               <msContents>
                  <summary>Mǝ‘raf Chants, ምዕራፍ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="94r" facs="003">Fols 1r–94r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3186Meeraf">Mǝʿrāf</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ምዕራፍ፡ በኵሉ፡ መዋዕል፡ እምዮሐንስ፡ እስከ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ዘጌና፡ ቅዱስ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ኃያል፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሕያው፡ ዘኢይመውት፡ ዘተወለደ፡ እማርያም፡ እምቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ ተሠሃለነ፡ እግዚኦ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <note>(using the foliation of the manuscript)</note>
                    <notatedMusic><desc>with musical notation</desc></notatedMusic>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="94r" facs="096">f. 94r, col. 2, bottom</locus><locus to="96r"/><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2610Zemmar">Zǝmmāre</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
